        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dr Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">I have just received<lb/> an order from <persName>Benj
                    Nathan</persName><lb/>
                <add>?</add> for one of your<lb/> Daily Prayer books, bound<lb/> and lettered like
                the Bible<lb/> I purchased for him on<lb/> his last birth day. I must<lb/> depend on
                your memory<lb/> for the style of the binding<lb/> I think it was dark<lb/> Morocco,
                with his name<lb/> on the side. Will you<lb/> also be so good as to tell<lb/> me
                whether the <date>20th Elul</date><lb/> will be on <date>Sunday</date> or
                    <date>Monday</date>?</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>I hope your health is<lb/> completely returned I<lb/> am sincerely</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Yours resptly</p>
            <p><date>Friday</date> Morning</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <date>Sept 12th 1862</date>
            </p>
        </body>
